                  +------+----------------+----+
                         |                |
                  I-side |                | D-side
                         v                v
              +----------------+     +------------------+
              |    I-Cache     |     |     D-Cache       |
              | Direct-Mapped  |     | Direct-Mapped     |
              | Miss/Refill FSM|     | Write-Through     |
              +-------+--------+     +---------+--------+
                      |                        |
                      v                        v
          Variable-Latency Instruction   Variable-Latency Data
                 Memory Model                Memory Model
```

