| `rv32i_regfile.sv` | 32-entry integer register file with x0 protection |
| `rv32i_decode.sv` | Instruction decode and control-signal generation |
| `rv32i_hazard_unit.sv` | Load-use hazard detection |
| `rv32i_forward_unit.sv` | EX/MEM and MEM/WB forwarding select generation |
| `rv32i_mem_unit.sv` | Variable-latency load/store transaction handling |
| `rv32i_icache.sv` | Direct-mapped instruction cache with miss/refill FSM |
| `rv32i_dcache.sv` | Direct-mapped write-through data cache |
| `rv32i_core.sv` | Top-level 5-stage RV32I CPU core |
| `design.sv` | Top-level include wrapper for EDA Playground compilation |
| `testbench.sv` | UVM environment, memory models, cache coverage, assertions, and directed stimulus |

