## 12. How to Run on EDA Playground

### 12.1 Required Files

```text
design.sv
testbench.sv
rv32i_pkg.sv
rv32i_alu.sv
rv32i_regfile.sv
rv32i_decode.sv
rv32i_hazard_unit.sv
rv32i_forward_unit.sv
rv32i_mem_unit.sv
rv32i_icache.sv
rv32i_dcache.sv
rv32i_core.sv
run.do
```

### 12.2 Compile Define

```text
+define+TB_LOADS_PROGRAM
```

### 12.3 Example Compile Command

```bash
vlib work && vlog '-sv2k12' '-timescale' '1ns/1ps' '+define+TB_LOADS_PROGRAM' \
+incdir+$RIVIERA_HOME/vlib/uvm-1800.2-2017/src \
-l uvm_1800_2_2017 \
design.sv testbench.sv && vsim -c -do run.do
```

### 12.4 Example run.do

```tcl
vsim work.tb_top +access+r
run -all
exit
```

